the infants, children and adolescents living in northwest Illinois. David Deutsch, MD Contact: David Deutsch, MD Chair, Department of Pediatrics tel. (815) 971-7667 Office Location: 8201 E. Riverside Blvd. Rockford, IL 61114 Campus mail for Dr. Deutsch can be left in the Dean’s Office, S201A Department Directory Departments Academic Departments Biomedical Sciences Directory Biomedical Sciences Adjunct Faculty Biomedical Research Faculty Regenerative Medicine and Disability Research Laboratory Research People Publications Useful Links News Contacts Biomedical Sciences Summer Programs SMART Program Family and Community Medicine Family Medicine Clerkship Medicine and Medical Specialties Medicine Clerkship Obstetrics and Gynecology OB/Gyn Faculty Pathology Pathology Medical Education Pathology Clerkship Pediatrics MERIT Ways to Help MERIT Psychiatry Teaching Activities Surgery and Surgical Specialties Centers About  Education  Research  Patient Care  Departments  News  Giving INFORMATION FOR: Prospective and Current Students  Faculty & Staff  Alumni & Friends  Patients  Businesses and Community RESOURCES: UIC Directory  Blackboard  Emergency Information  Contact Us  Apply Now  Give  Contact Us Connect with us!    If you have questions, comments, or problems accessing this site, please E-mail the webmaster  © Copyright 2019 University of Illinois College of Medicine   | Privacy Statement College of Medicine | Chicago | Peoria | Rockford | Urbana                                                                                                                                               